channel.title: Vampire's XpGainer
channel.description: This is XpGainer for a Myspace app. Vampires. Must have done mission for it to pick up. I sugest having screen resolution of 1024x768 or higher. Xp gained info is set for "Fight a Sewer Wererat" for start. There is a option for how many times to repeat a misson. If you decide to use something other then "Fight a Sewer Wererat" You can change xp gained status. Pick how many minutes and seconds between clicks, Have both set for 0 for normal clicking. This is the first usefull script Iv made.
